# Up-Down Counter

## Overview
Implements a counter that increments or decrements based on a control input.

## Board
Arty A7 (Artix-7)

## Tools
- Verilog
- Xilinx Vivado

## Description
The counter increases or decreases its value depending on the control signal. The output is displayed using LEDs.

## Inputs
- Clock
- Reset
- Direction control (Up/Down)

## Outputs
- LED output (counter value)

## Notes
Demonstrates basic sequential logic and control-based state changes.
